# Raw real-voice recordings used to retrain the "Hey CJ" classifier
# are too large + speaker-specific to ship in the repo. The trained
# classifier (app/wake/models/hey_cj.onnx) is what's committed.
#
# - real_raw/         operator-recorded WAVs (~10 MB each)
# - real_split/       per-utterance splits produced by phase1_split.py
# - real_positives/   final 16 kHz mono positives ready for training

real_raw/
real_split/
real_positives/
*.wav
